data.title: Pueblerina Original 1955 East German A1 Movie Poster
data.meta_description: Original 1955 East German A1 poster by Werner Klemke for the 1949 film Pueblerina (Paloma) directed by Emilio Fernandez with Columba Dominguez / Roberto Canedo / Arturo Soto Rangel / Manuel Donde.
